{"tid":1458642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日去機場，拖唔拖喼好","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:40.000Z","uid":113980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e86f38cf1d34234cea54dd750e5d39112467f708","tid":1458642,"uid":113980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"如果冇旅客=班狗可以清場=要散水<br />\n聽日最安全係唔係有班要離境嘅旅客陪我地一齊留<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">趕絕散水撚</span></span><br />\n仲有咁多旅客等緊車啊，等緊搭飛機啊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你同我講散水？</span></span><br />\n大家話拖唔拖喼好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a77c34ade053c91ddbb447d2d59b1861e44011","tid":1458642,"uid":113980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:34:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c34ec0aaab26135c460546cd06eedec25250a204","tid":1458642,"uid":113980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a68c739493bcf947ffdb72242379d34989528c","tid":1458642,"uid":113980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772da3c1a0011ced6074831e4029aaa4a60c741f","tid":1458642,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a5348cef5352079beeddd60d4dbaf8444a0358f","tid":1458642,"uid":4948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/